Package net.protheos.graph.demos

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DynamicMetric
    This demo main aim is to show how to execute a metric on a dynamic graph.
    Filtering
    This demo shows how to create and execute filter queries.
    GenerateGraph
    Demo how to generate a graph with generators.
    HeadlessSimple
    This demo shows several actions done with the toolkit, aiming to do a complete chain, from data import to results.
    ImportDynamic
    This demo shows how to create a dynamic network from a set of 'static' files using the DynamicProcessor (Time Frame Import).
    ImportExport
    This demo focuses on Import and Export features, showing different IO possibilities.
    Main  
    ManipulateAttributes
    Shows how to manipulate attributes.
    ManualGraph
    This demo shows basic features from GraphAPI, how to create and query a graph programmatically.
    MYSQLImportExport
    This demo shows how to import data from a MySQL database.
    ParallelWorkspace
    Demo about manipulating several workspaces.
    PartitionGraph
    This demo shows how to get partitions and apply color transformation to them.
    PreviewJFrame  
    RankingGraph
    The demo shows how to do ranking, transform colors and size according to degree or attribute values.
    WithAutoLayout
    This demo shows how to use the AutoLayout class to run layout programmatically.
